Intrigue Mission #1: A Blade in the Dark
GM Note: This is a solo spotlight mission for Orion, triggered during the Order of Business in Solitude if he chooses to follow the Dark Brotherhood's summons. It is a high-stakes test of stealth, strategy, and moral choice.
Part I: The Summons
Trigger: Orion chooses to attend the midnight meeting at the Hall of the Dead in Solitude.
